Ginga NEWS

* Version 1.1, 2022-today

  - Support WebServices for media control
  - Support CMake-based build
  - Drop support Autotools build
  - Improve GStreamer backend
  - Improve win deploy

* Version 1.0, 2015-2022

  - Support Autotools build
  - New Formmater as a reactive-based engine
  - New backend using gstreamer and GTK
  - Drop support processing transport stream files and run ncl files from it


* Version 0.13.6, 2010-2015

  - Backend using ffmpeg and SDL
  - Formmater as an callback-thread-based engine
  - Support running ncl documents from file
  - Support processing transport stream files and run ncl files from it